--[[
  Panda Alts 🐼 — Follow + Attack + Auto-Press (Client-Only)
  - Follow and Attack are mutually exclusive.
  - Attack includes an auto-press (exactly one input): Mouse1, Mouse2, or a single KeyCode.
  - Rate slider (5–15 presses/sec) and a brief start delay to avoid re-toggling when using Mouse1.
  - Draggable, compact UI with minimize and hard close.
  - Re-inject safe: re-running replaces previous instance cleanly.
  - Team Attack mode (targets players by team name).
  - Behavior: All attack modes and follow are toggled off on death/respawn.
  - Commander command listener (TextChatService) with UI textbox and toggle.
  - Commands: .atk/.attack, .follow/.goto, .hold, .stop, .atk random, .atk others, .atk all/everyone
  - Fixes:
    * Only press "1" to equip slot-1 tool when a tool exists in slot 1 and is not already equipped.
    * Commander handling: newest commander command HARD overrides previous commands.
    * .follow me and .goto me paste the commander's username into the follow textbox and follow that player.
    * When following a fragment, the follow textbox is filled with the matched player's full username.
    * Robust override: each commander command increments a session token so any older running routines immediately stop, preventing jitter between overlapping commands.
    * Additional safety: after hard-override, the handler briefly yields and re-checks the session token so only the most recent command proceeds — this guarantees older, near-simultaneous messages cannot continue and cause jitter.
]]

